snippet.title: CODE VEIN - Behind the Scenes 1 | X1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
From the story to the combat style, the #CODEVEIN dev team reveals their inspirations creating this dungeon-crawler, action RPG!

Learn more about CODE VEIN, our newest title currently being developed by the team who brought you #GodEater: https://bandainam.co/codevein
